{"tid":1903334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄︰4月20日之後是否復課仍要留意疫情發展！","createTime":"2020-02-29T01:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T04:06:38.000Z","uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a48d7da2addecf7f3ff470fe1dd5104247ea7df3","tid":1903334,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T01:38:18.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄表示，在4月20日之後是否復課，仍然會密切留意新型肺炎疫情發展，以及學校準備工作和社會防疫物資是否足夠。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄出席一個電台節目時，又回應下月27日開始考文憑試的問題，認為必須有足夠安全度的環境去考試，否則會令學生冒險，因為考試期間仍然停課，可以盡用課室空間，去拉闊考生之後的空間。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，目標是考生間的距離達1.8米，雖然每間學校環境有不同，不能一定做到，但至少會有超過1米距離。所以考慮種種因素後，決定下月27日開考，令放榜以至外地升學等可維持原有安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511590-20200229.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511590-20200229.htm&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT2zMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=b929c1de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511590-20200229.htm&h=15b568ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511590-20200229.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f4b2b875748f682627a84270df489fff0c2ec925","tid":1903334,"uid":63113,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T01:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bdpbmuh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdpbmuh.gif&h=e320aa5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a79999eac6249e71744fcd16bd659fdcd94acb6","tid":1903334,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T01:39:08.000Z","msg":"復唔到啦 一日不封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最新觀點：五大訴求唔包括爭取功能組別架！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1903326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1903326</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"447566bfec647a321c778e74de64811d0c0a9af7","tid":1903334,"uid":75479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4b2b875748f